# Open-in-installed-app prompt

Full doc: [docs/pwa-open-in-app.md](../../docs/pwa-open-in-app.md).

Protect these invariants:

- On member tab routes, the dock MUST sit above the bottom nav via
  `bottom-[var(--bottom-nav-height)]`.
- Android **Open in app** must call `openInstalledPwa()` →
  `window.open(inScopeHttpsUrl, '_blank', 'noopener,noreferrer')`. Never
  `location.assign`, SPA navigation, `web+pushus://`, or intent fallback URLs.
- iOS: home-screen instructions only — no fake open button.
- Suppress when `display-mode: standalone`.
- `index.html` links `rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json"`.
- `related_applications` uses `platform: "webapp"` and `url: "/manifest.json"`.

Run `npm test` and keep `tests/unit/pwaOpenAppPrompt.test.ts` and
`tests/unit/pwaOpenInApp.test.ts` green.
